#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:2
#: b5ec1d592dc142c393dd1514fe7b7f88
msgid "Hertzian Contact"
msgstr "赫兹接触"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:4
#: e98d321f0fca439eba9f89f4cf2a3085
msgid ""
"A 2D contact-mechanics problem: a circular elastic indenter is pressed into "
"a rectangular elastic block; the contact pressure along the interface should"
" match the analytical Hertz solution. The script "
"``examples/solid/hertzian_contact/hertzian_contact.py`` solves it with a "
"**penalty method** — the contact constraint is enforced by adding a "
"quadratic penalty energy to the total potential, then minimized with L-BFGS."
msgstr ""
"一个二维接触力学问题：一个圆形弹性压头被压入一块矩形弹性体；界面上的接触压力应当与赫兹解析解相吻合。脚本 "
"``examples/solid/hertzian_contact/hertzian_contact.py`` 用 **罚函数法** "
"求解——通过向总势能中添加一个二次罚能量来施加接触约束，然后用 L-BFGS 最小化。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:14
#: 75c2fbe343bf448a8980ccfb8f90e539
msgid "Problem"
msgstr "问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:16
#: b28569344cbd4ed8b3121577027523ef
msgid "Two linear-elastic bodies (:math:`E = 1000` Pa, :math:`\\nu = 0.3`):"
msgstr "两个线弹性物体（\\ :math:`E = 1000` Pa，\\ :math:`\\nu = 0.3`\\ ）："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:18
#: 4511f16b246546d3a5fb1f526085053c
msgid ""
"**Indenter** — full circular disc of radius :math:`R = 1.0`, meshed with "
"Tri6 quadratic triangles, centered at :math:`(-1.0, 0)` so the right-most "
"point sits at the origin. Its left-most arc (:math:`x < -1.8`) is clamped."
msgstr ""
"**压头** —— 半径为 :math:`R = 1.0` 的完整圆盘，用 Tri6 二次三角形单元划分网格，圆心位于 :math:`(-1.0, "
"0)`\\ ，使其最右端点恰好位于原点。其最左侧的弧段（\\ :math:`x < -1.8`\\ ）被固定。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:22
#: e84aa7807f994094bd550535459ac92b
msgid ""
"**Block** — rectangle :math:`[0, 1] \\times [-1, 1]`, meshed with Quad9 "
"quadratic quadrilaterals. The right edge (:math:`x = 1`) has prescribed "
"displacement :math:`u_x = -0.15` (pushing left, into the indenter)."
msgstr ""
"**弹性体** —— 矩形 :math:`[0, 1] \\times [-1, 1]`\\ ，用 Quad9 二次四边形单元划分网格。右边缘（\\ "
":math:`x = 1`\\ ）施加规定位移 :math:`u_x = -0.15`\\ （向左推，压向压头）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:27
#: 195c9befd21c43c7893af88f884f5c56
msgid ""
"The contact interface is the vertical line :math:`x = 0`. As the block moves"
" leftward the indenter is compressed, and a contact patch forms."
msgstr "接触界面是竖直线 :math:`x = 0`\\ 。随着弹性体向左移动，压头被压缩，并形成接触斑。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:33
#: 480b2f9de97e49178c01783cbf5eabf4
msgid "Penalty contact"
msgstr "罚函数接触"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:35
#: 81255e1ce25b4b71a1be7308c1d2d22d
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Frictionless normal contact is the constraint :math:`g(\\mathbf{x}) \\geq "
"0`, where :math:`g` is the **gap function** (signed distance between the two"
" surfaces, positive when separated). The penalty method replaces the "
"inequality constraint by the contact energy"
msgstr ""
"无摩擦法向接触是约束 :math:`g(\\mathbf{x}) \\geq 0`\\ ，其中 :math:`g` 是 **间隙函数**\\ "
"（两个表面之间的有符号距离，分离时为正）。罚函数法用接触能量来代替这一不等式约束"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:41
#: e1775c359da4404695e6031a5c4843f5
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"E_\\text{contact}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\frac{1}{2}\\, k_p \\int_{\\Gamma_c}\n"
"\\langle -g \\rangle_+^2 \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Gamma,"
msgstr ""
"E_\\text{contact}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\frac{1}{2}\\, k_p \\int_{\\Gamma_c}\n"
"\\langle -g \\rangle_+^2 \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Gamma,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:48
#: 3d031ef6def54948b3732a5c2aa45534
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\langle x \\rangle_+ = \\max(x, 0)` and :math:`k_p = 2 \\times"
" 10^6` is the penalty stiffness. As :math:`k_p \\to \\infty` the constraint "
"is enforced exactly, but the problem becomes ill-conditioned; in practice "
":math:`k_p` is chosen to be a few orders of magnitude larger than the "
"elastic stiffness."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`\\langle x \\rangle_+ = \\max(x, 0)`\\ ，\\ :math:`k_p = 2 \\times "
"10^6` 是罚刚度。当 :math:`k_p \\to \\infty` 时约束被精确施加，但问题会变得病态；实际中 :math:`k_p` "
"通常取为比弹性刚度大几个数量级。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:55
#: ec68f399c8714bd9aef23db35107cff4
msgid "The total energy minimized at each L-BFGS step is"
msgstr "在每个 L-BFGS 步中被最小化的总能量为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:57
#: 6f65c18ada0243c2a51cba685963f94e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\Pi(\\mathbf{u})\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\int_{\\Omega_1} \\tfrac12 \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_1 : \\mathbb{C} : \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_1\n"
"\\;+\\;\n"
"\\int_{\\Omega_2} \\tfrac12 \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_2 : \\mathbb{C} : \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_2\n"
"\\;+\\;\n"
"E_\\text{contact}."
msgstr ""
"\\Pi(\\mathbf{u})\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\int_{\\Omega_1} \\tfrac12 \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_1 : \\mathbb{C} : \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_1\n"
"\\;+\\;\n"
"\\int_{\\Omega_2} \\tfrac12 \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_2 : \\mathbb{C} : \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}_2\n"
"\\;+\\;\n"
"E_\\text{contact}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:67
#: 6feec80ff4d9446992a610fc6e3c6237
msgid ""
"The first two terms come from "
":class:`~tensormesh.LinearElasticityElementAssembler` 's energy form (small-"
"strain quadratic energy); the contact term is implemented separately in the "
"script."
msgstr ""
"前两项来自 :class:`~tensormesh.LinearElasticityElementAssembler` "
"的能量形式（小应变二次能量）；接触项则在脚本中单独实现。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:74
#: fdaa0feceb14491aac8216a8c34d134d
msgid "Point-to-segment detection"
msgstr "点对段检测"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:76
#: 4a62436b073f4b96bc426f49834eceda
msgid ""
"The interface :math:`\\Gamma_c` is partitioned into \"slave nodes\" on one "
"body and \"master segments\" on the other. For each slave node, the script "
"projects onto the closest master segment, computes the signed normal gap, "
"and accumulates the penalty contribution."
msgstr ""
"界面 :math:`\\Gamma_c` "
"被划分为一个物体上的“从节点”和另一个物体上的“主段”。对每个从节点，脚本将其投影到最近的主段上，计算有符号的法向间隙，并累加罚函数贡献。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:81
#: 5b9bb56ae0934fa5a553018c29ca9207
msgid ""
"The script does this **two-way** (each body's interface nodes are slaves "
"with respect to the other body) which gives a symmetric formulation and "
"avoids the bias of a one-master-one-slave choice."
msgstr "脚本采用 **双向** 处理（每个物体的界面节点相对于另一个物体都作为从节点），这给出了对称的表述，并避免了单主单从选择所带来的偏差。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:87
#: ee34d7f68eb74c2889bc435c17b7e83f
msgid "Energy minimization with L-BFGS"
msgstr "用 L-BFGS 进行能量最小化"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:89
#: fdc858f2928b49a18ed3b00dbed03ed5
msgid ""
"The pattern is the one introduced in :doc:`hyperelastic_beam`: a single "
"``u`` parameter for both meshes, BCs enforced inside the closure, autograd "
"providing the gradient. The contact term is re-evaluated every iteration "
"because the gap function depends on the current configuration:"
msgstr ""
"这一模式与 :doc:`hyperelastic_beam` 中介绍的相同：两个网格共用一个 ``u`` 参数，边界条件在闭包内部施加，由 "
"autograd 提供梯度。由于间隙函数依赖于当前构型，接触项在每次迭代中都会重新计算："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:95
#: 023c0d8abcab48f8824197892b056781
msgid "examples/solid/hertzian_contact/hertzian_contact.py (sketch)"
msgstr "examples/solid/hertzian_contact/hertzian_contact.py（示意）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:113
#: a296b295312044a589a03312f2e8ec53
msgid "Comparison with the Hertz analytical solution"
msgstr "与赫兹解析解的对比"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:115
#: 313560b6c79d4ff2b81a68b79ff32b19
msgid ""
"For 2D plane-strain contact between an elastic cylinder and a half-space, "
"Hertz theory gives a parabolic pressure distribution:"
msgstr "对于弹性圆柱与半空间之间的二维平面应变接触，赫兹理论给出抛物线形的压力分布："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:118
#: 1659aadf4fa64cb48b5763db9a284b5e
msgid ""
"p(x) \\;=\\; p_\\text{max}\\, \\sqrt{1 - (x / a)^2},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"p_\\text{max} = \\sqrt{\\frac{P\\, E^*}{\\pi\\, R^*}},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"a = \\sqrt{\\frac{4 P\\, R^*}{\\pi\\, E^*}},"
msgstr ""
"p(x) \\;=\\; p_\\text{max}\\, \\sqrt{1 - (x / a)^2},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"p_\\text{max} = \\sqrt{\\frac{P\\, E^*}{\\pi\\, R^*}},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"a = \\sqrt{\\frac{4 P\\, R^*}{\\pi\\, E^*}},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:126
#: 0d0486e506cf47b6aa9db4b1c0225941
msgid ""
"with effective modulus :math:`E^*` and effective radius :math:`R^*` derived "
"from the two-body geometry. The script extracts the contact pressure from "
"the converged solution and overlays it on the analytical curve in "
"``hertzian_contact.png`` — the FEM match is good once the mesh is fine "
"enough near the contact patch (``chara_length=0.1`` is a reasonable starting"
" point)."
msgstr ""
"其中等效模量 :math:`E^*` 和等效半径 :math:`R^*` 由两体几何导出。脚本从收敛解中提取接触压力，并将其叠加到 "
"``hertzian_contact.png`` 中的解析曲线上——只要接触斑附近的网格足够细，有限元结果就吻合得很好（\\ "
"``chara_length=0.1`` 是一个合理的起点）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:133
#: 6143fa2470e64c189264f6358f5292a7
msgid "Hertzian contact von Mises stress field"
msgstr "赫兹接触的冯·米塞斯应力场"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:137
#: fd965ac04d8e47ca84c8fe54851014e8
msgid ""
"Output of ``hertzian_contact.py``: von Mises stress field on the deformable "
"indenter (circle) pressed against the displaced block (right). Stress "
"concentrates in a roughly teardrop-shaped region inside the indenter, "
"centered just inboard of the contact patch — the classical Hertzian "
"subsurface stress distribution. The fixed left wall and prescribed "
"displacement arrows on the right block illustrate the boundary setup."
msgstr ""
"``hertzian_contact.py`` "
"的输出：可变形压头（圆形）压向被位移的弹性体（右侧）时的冯·米塞斯应力场。应力集中在压头内部一个大致呈泪滴形的区域中，其中心略微位于接触斑内侧——这是经典的赫兹次表面应力分布。左侧固定壁和右侧弹性体上的规定位移箭头展示了边界设置。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/hertzian_contact.rst:148
#: 5049a1eb34be447ea45c075c95810d87
